<h2 id="tricky-adjectives">Tricky Adjectives That Fool Learners</h2>

<div style="background:#fef3c7; border:1px solid #fde68a; border-radius:12px; padding:1.5rem; margin:1.5rem 0;">
  <p style="font-weight:700; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">na-Adjectives That Look Like i-Adjectives</p>
